<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><recipe><recipe-name>Dark Broth Crockpot Ramen</recipe-name><description>Authentic Ramen done in a crockpot. This is a dark/acidic broth.</description><ingredients><Ingredient><ingredient-name>Chicken Breast</ingredient-name><amount>1</amount><measurement>lb</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>Yellow onion</ingredient-name><amount>0.5</amount><measurement>onion</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>Garlic</ingredient-name><amount>3</amount><measurement>cloves</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>chicken broth</ingredient-name><amount>4</amount><measurement>cups</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>soy sauce</ingredient-name><amount>0.25</amount><measurement>cups</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>seasoned rice vinegar</ingredient-name><amount>0.25</amount><measurement>cups</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>unsweetened soy milk</ingredient-name><amount>0.5</amount><measurement>cups</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>sliced mushrooms</ingredient-name><amount>4</amount><measurement>oz</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>ground ginger</ingredient-name><amount>0.5</amount><measurement>tsp</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>black pepper</ingredient-name><amount>0.5</amount><measurement>tsp</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>ramen noodles</ingredient-name><amount>6</amount><measurement>oz</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>crushed red pepper</ingredient-name><amount>2</amount><measurement>pinches</measurement></Ingredient><Ingredient><ingredient-name>sliced jalepenos</ingredient-name><amount>2</amount><measurement>jaleps</measurement></Ingredient><instructions>Place chicken, onion, garlic, broth, soy sauce, vinegar, milk, mushrooms, ginger, and pepper into crockpot. Cover and cook on low for 3 hours. After 3 hours, remove chicken and let rest. Place crockpot to high and stir in ramen noodles. Cover and let cook for 5-10 minutes. Thinly slice chicken and place back into broth. Top with optional ingredients and serve.</instructions></ingredients></recipe>